    {
      "turn_id": 2,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "clarify",
      "utterance": "明白了。我注意到CustomCli和CustomApi都关联到FinTech_LedgerService，而CustomApp和CustomSdk都关联到FinTech_TransactionQueue。CustomLib则是FinTech_PaymentGateway对吧？",
      "elements_involved": [
