    {
      "turn_id": 3,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "对的。另外SDK和API之间的通信比较复杂：SDK发bRequest消息给API，这个请求会经过FinTech_FraudDetection风控检测，然后API返回bResponse消息给SDK，响应由FinTech_LedgerService处理。",
