    {
      "turn_id": 4,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "execute",
      "utterance": "好的，我先画出五层组件，标注好各自的FinTech业务域。然后画SDK到API的双向消息流，bRequest带风控，bResponse带账本服务。",
      "elements_involved": [
